  <summary>7/31/1996--Introduced.
Amends Federal law to require the Federal Acquisition Regulation to ensure avoidance of unnecessary bundling of contract requirements. Amends the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act to revise the definition of "bundling of contract requirements." Provides for the reporting of bundled contract opportunities.</summary>
